ZH: 暴雨导致城市发生了严重的涝害。
EN: The heavy rain caused serious flooding in the city.

ZH: 这次洪水导致许多农田被淹没，造成了严重的涝情。
EN: The flood caused many farmlands to be submerged, resulting in severe flooding.

ZH: 增加排水能力是减少涝害的有效措施之一。
EN: Increasing drainage capacity is one effective measure to reduce flooding.

ZH: 在暴雨来临前及时清理下水道可以有效预防涝情。
EN: Clearing the drains in time before the heavy rain arrives can effectively prevent flooding.

ZH: 大型的水利工程可以有效地解决河流涝情的问题。
EN: Large-scale water conservancy projects can effectively solve the problem of river flooding.

ZH: 农田中的排水系统应该得到及时的维护，以防止涝害发生。
EN: The drainage system in farmland should be maintained in a timely manner to prevent flooding.

ZH: 学校应该制定应急预案，在发生涝害时及时采取措施保障学生安全。
EN: Schools should formulate emergency plans to take timely measures to ensure the safety of students in case of flooding.

ZH: 暴雨过后，城市的一些地区出现了严重的涝害。
EN: After the heavy rain, some areas of the city experienced serious flooding.

ZH: 水库溃坝导致了周边地区的大面积涝害。
EN: The dam failure led to widespread flooding in the surrounding areas.

ZH: 地势低洼的地区容易发生涝害。
EN: Low-lying areas are prone to flooding.

ZH: 湖泊水位上涨，可能引发淹没周边村庄的涝情。
EN: The rise in lake water levels may cause flooding in surrounding villages.

ZH: 在暴雨过后，城市各处都有涝害发生。
EN: After the heavy rain, flooding occurred in various parts of the city.

ZH: 在水利工程的支持下，这个地区成功解决了长期以来的涝害问题。
EN: With the support of water conservancy projects, this area successfully solved the long-standing flooding problem.

ZH: 防范涝害需要政府、社会和个人的共同努力。
EN: Preventing flooding requires the joint efforts of the government, society, and individuals.

ZH: 根据气象预报，这周可能会出现暴雨，需要提前做好防范涝害的准备。
EN: According to the weather forecast, heavy rain may occur this week, so preparations need to be made in advance to prevent flooding.

ZH: 平时应该做好地势低洼地区的排水工作，以减少涝害发生的可能性。
EN: Drainage work should be done in low-lying areas at ordinary times to reduce the possibility of flooding.

ZH: 洪水来袭时，我们应该保持警觉，及时采取措施避免涝情带来的危害。
EN: When floods strike, we should remain vigilant and take timely measures to avoid the harm caused by flooding.

ZH: 这次涝害给城市造成了不小的损失，需要加强预防工作。
EN: The flooding caused considerable losses to the city, so preventive efforts need to be strengthened.

ZH: 水位上涨导致河堤决口，引发了大面积的涝害。
EN: Rising water levels caused the riverbank to breach, triggering widespread flooding.
